snippet.title: Gateway to the Savage Frontier gameplay (PC Game, 1991)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Gateway to the Savage Frontier, Dos PC game produced by SSI in 1991 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/gateway-to-the-savage-frontier/4038/
Creating some characters and engaging in combat in this fantasy adventure.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
